column2: SELECT ALL m.OBJID AS akari_ID, m.RA AS akari_ra, m.DEC AS akari_dec, o.z AS redshift, o.zErr AS err_redshift, o.class, o.modelMag_u AS u, o.modelMag_g AS g, o.modelMag_r AS r, o.modelMag_i AS i, o.modelMag_z AS z, o.modelMagErr_u AS uErr, o.modelMagErr_g AS gErr, o.modelMagErr_r AS rErr, o.modelMagErr_i AS iErr, o.modelMagErr_z AS zErr, n.objid, n.distance into mydb.outputSubset1# from MyDB.akari1# AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjAllEq (m.RA, m.DEC, #) AS n JOIN SpecPhoto AS o ON n.objid = o.specObjID
